snippet.title: Pool Nation FX Steam Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Free-to-play Lite version of Pool Nation FX coming to Steam December 7th 2015. 
The F2P version will include, limitless online 8 Ball pool, an offline practice mode, a Daily Bonus Match and full access to the customisable features including cues, balls, decals and locations unlockable by an in game currency Pool Nation Dollars.
